---
title: Glazed Plant-Based Ground Protein Meatballs with Loaded Potato Wedges and Side Salad
description: Get a load of this meal! BBQ sauce-slathered  plant-based ground protein meatballs and loaded potato wedges come together for a delightful explosion of flavours. Grab some napkins and dig in!
